lead_paragraph: On a night when the starters for both teams spent most of the night on the sideline, Seattle running back Thomas Rawls made a big statement by getting on the field for only a few plays.

headline.print_headline: Seahawks Close Exhibition Season With 23-21 Win Over Raiders
